version_description: Thanks to this update. The latest version contains experience improvements and bug fixes.

1. Add guideline to search page to let users know better how to browse more photos.
2. Fix a bug for message part if the connection is bad or lost.
3. Improve the Likes part experience and some other experience improvements.

• Fixed the crash bug to match with the newest system iOS 13.4 
• Fixed a minor issue of "Apple ID Login". 
• Performance enhancements.

• Improve the process of verification and add one more benefit for verified members.
• Allow members to change main photo if they only have one profile photo. 
• Regular maintenance and minor improvements.
